{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_013ooWWzmiCs1VRBq3BP85P3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01HaHJoE3M7oWYD8GwitwFDo","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Architecture & code quality review","subagent_type":"code-review-expert","prompt":"Review architecture and code quality of the iteration 26 changes in the title-extractor.\n\n## Context\n- Compare against the improvement plan at tools/title-loop/docs/26-e8ee23c/improvement-plan.md\n- Focus on lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts and lib/text-classifier/food-dictionary.ts\n\n## What was changed (from git diff HEAD~1):\n\n### food-dictionary.ts\n- Added ~30 common title words to FOOD_DICTIONARY (prepositions, adjectives, Polish words)\n\n### title-extractor.ts\n- New `CATEGORY_SECTION_LABELS` set — duplicates subset of `SECTION_LABELS`\n- New `isCategorySectionLabel()` function\n- New `extractContentWords()` + `passesCorroboration()` — vocabulary corroboration\n- New `isBodyProse()` — lowercase prose detection\n- Modified `startsWithNumber` — Unicode fractions\n- Modified `isTitleAbsentPage` — body prose detection\n- Modified `findBurstEnd` — improved spillover handling\n- Modified caps-coalescing merge condition\n- Modified first-after-preamble bonus logic\n- Added pre-threshold artifact filtering\n- Modified multi-title assembly with corroboration\n\n## Architecture & quality focus:\n1. **Duplication**: `CATEGORY_SECTION_LABELS` overlaps significantly with `SECTION_LABELS`. Should `CATEGORY_SECTION_LABELS` be derived from `SECTION_LABELS`? Could they drift apart?\n2. **Function placement**: Are new functions placed logically in the file?\n3. **passesCorroboration** is called in two separate places (pre-threshold ~line 1210 and multi-title ~line 1400). Is this redundant? Should it be called once and cached?\n4. **Complexity growth**: The file is already large. Do these changes push it toward needing a refactor?\n5. **Naming**: Are `CATEGORY_SECTION_LABELS`, `passesCorroboration`, `isBodyProse`, `extractContentWords` well-named?\n6. **The improvement plan** specified 5 fixes. Were all implemented? Were any implemented differently than planned?\n\nRead the actual source files and improvement plan to verify. Return specific findings with file:line references."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":9577,"cache_read_input_tokens":43269,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":9577},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"80bb29ff-3467-4b06-a8e7-a7aec63d83fa","uuid":"e74623f7-ceb6-47b6-a12c-0d4b2950af9f"}
